name: Removing the veil of the lonelinest city

metadata.name: Nightcrawler
metadata.description:
How I can reveal how hufe the city is? I wanted to show another side of Tokyo to the busy, tourist side we learn about. There's another side I was trying to look for. 

This serie of photos explains how frightening and isolating life can ve in one of the safest and most populated cities in the world; a city in contradicion to the only one I've ever known.
